==English==
===Intransitive verb phrase===
'''to fall in love''' (''past tense'' '''fell in love''', ''past participle'' '''fallen in love''')

#Of a person, to come to have feelings of [[romantic love]] directed at (another person or a thing).
#(''[[reciprocal]]'') Of two people, to come to have feelings of romantic love towards each other.

